# itypes

## Types

* Uint32s | []uint32
* Uints | []uint
* Ints | []int
* Int64s | []int64
* Strings | []string

## Features

function|output|input types
:-:|:-:|:-:
ToInt | int, error | ints, string
ToInt64 | int64, error | ints, string
ToFloat64 | int64, error | floats, ints, string
IntToString | string, error | ints, uints
HideString | xxx | string
